        "subject": "LU-12678 lnet: lnet_startup_lndnet: avoid use-after-free",
        "message": "LU-12678 lnet: lnet_startup_lndnet: avoid use-after-free\n\nIf lnet_startup_lndni() fails it will free 'ni' (via lnet_ni_free()).\nSo we mustn't de-reference it in the LASSERT() in that case\n\nLustre-change: https://review.whamcloud.com/36855\nLustre-commit: 9136b90f4c643aefcb9fd65c4282b700874f0e90\n\nSigned-off-by: Mr NeilBrown <neilb@suse.de>\nChange-Id: I01e35013e028a8f95f169e25aeb0c344b2310380\nDDN-bug-id: DDN-3151\nSigned-off-by: Cyril Bordage <cbordage@whamcloud.com>\n"
      },
